Sentencas: A novel active cathode structure of La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.9Sc0.1O3-delta (LSFSc) infiltrated porous 8 mol%Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 (YSZ) was fabricated by tape casting, co-sintering and infiltration techniques.
Titulo: Infiltrated porous YSZ as a cathode active layer for cathode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The infiltrated porous-YSZ layer worked as a cathode active layer (CAL) between a YSZ electrolyte layer and (La0.8Sr0.2)(0.95)MnO3 (LSM95) cathode substrate.
Titulo: Infiltrated porous YSZ as a cathode active layer for cathode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The obtained fuel cells with Ni/SDC anode showed the maximum power densities of 0.574, 0.733 and 0.835 W.cm(-2) at 750, 800 and 850 degrees C, respectively, with H-2 as fuel and air as the oxidant.
Titulo: Infiltrated porous YSZ as a cathode active layer for cathode-supported solid oxide fuel cells
